VALUES
	(1,'1','1',NULL,'about us','img/contents/28d1153311b9dc57066718d80d9c4438.png','img/contents/27389729e971bd1c986337ba0e936196.png','Web are a company that is looking for a better problems approach, so we can guarantee a product which will fit exactly how the customer has thought. ','0','<p>Our company delivers scalable &amp; suitable digital solutions for small and big businesses. <span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>We love new challenges and we have a rare blend of both design</strong></span>, and development expertise that gives us the capabilities of building some complex and custom web features for our clients. We approach the business problem in a different way, so we are able to bring the solution that you have been thinking on.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>With our expertise spanning modern websites, e-commerce, and mobile-responsive front-end design, <strong><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">our clients can enjoy the full spectrum of the services that we offer in g-ocanto</span></strong>.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We guarantee you getting more from the website using high value web features and by creating a better user experience that improves conversions and adapts the website to meet your needs of your online gate.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We love your web presence. Also, we know that it is more important than ever before, and is integral to your ongoing success.<strong><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"> Let us help you successfully deliver the information your clients</span></strong> and employees need.</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-03 12:37:56',1,NULL,NULL),
	(49,'1','3',NULL,'Hungry for Retweets and Facebook Likes? Study Shows Best Times to Post','img/contents/dc9f441cdcb5438dd7894a80590603a8.jpg','img/contents/1c19984c3e03c6b169b9ef50faa1a0e2.jpg','Tuesdays and Wednesdays are the best days to post things if you want the maximum amount of likes, comments and retweets — late Tuesday and Wednesday morning, to be precise.','0','<p>Whether you&#39;re posting on social media personally or professionally, sometimes you really do want to maximize the reaction. New research has some straightforward advice for you.</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://arxiv.org/pdf/1506.02089v1.pdf\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(67, 114, 184); text-decoration: none; background: 0px 0px;\">A study (PDF)</a>&nbsp;by social media metric company Klout found that Tuesdays and Wednesdays are the best days to post things if you want the maximum amount of likes, comments and retweets &mdash; late Tuesday and Wednesday morning, to be precise.</p>\n\n<p>Related:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.nbcnews.com/news/us-news/snap-white-house-lifts-ban-photos-social-media-during-tours-n385051\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(67, 114, 184); text-decoration: none; background: 0px 0px;\">Snap! White House Lifts Ban on Photos, Social Media During Tours</a></p>\n\n<p>Chart showing likelihood of response to posts on Facebook (top) and Twitter (bottom) throughout the week - click the picture to expand to full size.&nbsp;Klout</p>\n\n<p>The researchers analyzed the reactions to 144 million posts on Facebook and Twitter, and found that there was a reliable improvement in engagement as the morning wore on &mdash; and just before lunchtime, posts were three or four times more likely to find an audience. This boost quickly disappears in the afternoon, though.</p>\n\n<p>Related:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/millennials-get-their-political-news-facebook-not-purpose-n367936\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(67, 114, 184); text-decoration: none; background: 0px 0px;\">Millennials Get Their Political News From Facebook - But Not on Purpose</a></p>\n\n<p>And what&#39;s the worst time to post? The weekend, surprisingly. Perhaps users are inundated with pictures of Friday night, or sleep in past the late-morning social media prime time.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Source</strong></p>\n\n<p>http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/social-media/want-more-likes-retweets-study-shows-best-times-get-them-n385926</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-05 05:37:40',NULL,NULL,NULL),
	(2,'1','1',NULL,'customers','img/settings.png',NULL,'Algunos de nuestros clientes','We love our field of work and we design with passion! A new project means a new challenge for us. We aim to make our clients happy and satisfied with a website that grows their business and not just an online gate.<br>','customers','','1',NULL,2,NULL,NULL),
	(3,'1','2',NULL,'services','img/design.png','img/contents/e5fd794de5c22a9e4b4fcc8f0b56a270.png','We are one stop solution agency for all of your creative and marketing requirements. We work hard to bring your business up online, so everybody around world can contact you anytime.','0','<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">UI/UX Design</span></h4>\n\n<p>Great user experience design comes from collaboration between world-class designers, experienced developers, and our customers. &nbsp;Our in-house creative design agency plays the lead role in that process of turning ideas into stunning UI/UX &amp; visual design.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>We specialize in:&nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>User experience design and development.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Usability testing and analysis.</li>\n	<li>Laravel Framework</li>\n	<li>Angular JS</li>\n	<li>Bootstrap CSS</li>\n	<li>And more</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Social Media Marketing</span><span style=\"color:rgb(106, 143, 48)\">&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>We develop and manage effective social media marketing programs that lift brand awareness, engaging with communities in your kind of industry and driving traffic to your website. We create and/or enhance your existing social media channels including Facebook, LinkedIn and Twitter, and we propel your organization down the right social media path with effective strategy, planning, participation and measurement.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Social media services include:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Social media marketing strategy.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Implementation guidelines.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Social media audit Competitive analysis.</li>\n	<li>Social profile creation.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Widget strategy development.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Blog design, setup and/or optimization.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Blog strategy development.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Community building strategy development.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Community monitoring.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Web and Mobile App&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Whether you are looking to optimise an existing intranet, to build a new one, or to develop workflows, our consultants, designers and developers are on hand. We will create knowledge sharing and collaboration applications that drive productivity, that inspire employee engagement, and deliver the return on investment.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Our development services include: &nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Intranet applications B2B/B2C.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>portals Social media.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>applications Mobile apps.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">E-commerce&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Online shopping are today firmly established, continually growing part of our economy. Online shoppers continue expecting more from their preferred online shopping websites about functionality, convenience and security. With robust E-Commerce development services from Sculpt Media.&nbsp;You can ensure that your customers are able to shop on your website with confidence and ease.</p>\n\n<p>Sculpt Media offers custom E-Commerce application development that ensures security and gives you the power to manage products, create modules relted to your sales and marketing strategy, connectivity with third-party CRM/ERP system, and provide business-critical reports on your website.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Our E-commerce service includes:&nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Store research and strategy.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Target market research.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Store design and development.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Store marketing and management.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Print and Branding&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Working from an outline&nbsp;brief, which is shared with groups of internal and external stakeholders, we provide creative concepts that will connect with your customers and employees. We will develop a unique and distinctive creative solution that keeps your distinct brand and ahead of your competitors. Once defined, we will produce brand guidelines&nbsp;to ensure consistency in all elements: starting with stationery, signage, and as well as both online and offline brand communications.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Our creative services include: &nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Logo design&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Identity and branding&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Corporate profile design&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Flyer and poster design&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Advertising campaign design</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">SEO&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>At Sculpt Media, we pride ourselves in utilizing the latest search engine optimization techniques and strategies, which are combined with in-depth internet expertise to deliver effective and improved search engine placements, while maintaining ethical optimization practices, for our client&#39;s companies. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Our SEO service includes:</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Initial site review and SEO analysis.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Keywords research and competitor analysis.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>SEO content writing.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Ranking monitoring and reporting.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Content Writing&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Content writing is about using the right words in the right way at the right time, to get the target audience, to take action, and make a purchase. Our copywriters are armed with the requisite skills and knowledge to build your brand and drive your sales up.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>We specialized in writing: &nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Blog posts.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Product descriptions.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Website content.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>SEO content.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Presentation content.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Press releases.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>White papers.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Newsletter content.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Animation</span>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<p>Sculpt Media excels in producing engaging interactive solutions that deliver results. &nbsp;We listen to your brief, research your audience, we select the correct media and create the perfect interactive solution for your requirement.</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>We specialize in: &nbsp;</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Interactive presentation.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Product tutorial.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>E-learning application.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Product Restructuring&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Businesses often need to modify their strategies to suit varying needs. To support enterprises in managing these challenges, we ensure companies properly weigh out the consequences of restructuring their product portfolios while we ascertain a comprehensive understanding of their business models.</p>\n\n<p>We support companies in redirecting their product and service offerings, such as we analyze their target markets and distribution strategies. By doing so, businesses will be able to balance between realising short-term objectives and investing in long-term performance. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<h5><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\"><strong>Our product restructuring service includes:</strong></span></h5>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Product strategy and planning.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Market due diligence.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Product monitoring and performance.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Web Hosting&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>We offer reliable and affordable php web hosting to worldwide users. By employing Sculpt Media your Web host, you can quickly, easily and affordably launch, run and maintain websites for your small to corporate size business. Our 24/7 network monitoring, 99.9% server uptime, and our always-on support team combine to produce rock-solid reliability.</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Web Domains</span></h4>\n\n<p>Online success starts with a great domain. At Domain.com, we make it easy and inexpensive to get the domain you want, fast. We offer all major Top Level Domains (TLDs) and over 25 Country Code Top Level Domains (ccTLDs). Every domain registration includes the following domain tools:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>URL Forwarding.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Email Forwarding.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>DNS Management.&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Transfer Lock Protect.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 16:37:26',3,NULL,NULL),
	(6,'2','1',NULL,'consulting','img/support.png','img/contents/9051ac5c8b1f9926b797ff9af88b49a9.png','Our approach comes from our belief that the sense of meaning in our lives comes from the work that we do and people we help. ','0','<p>We are a personal web consulting firm that specializes in creating and fixing websites to attract customers to your business.</p>\n\n<p>To dominate your competitors, your website must be appealing, unique, and rank at the top of Google. Our website services can help you set up your website properly and avoid costly mistakes. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Our consulting, web design, and search engine optimization (SEO) solutions will guarantee your business increased visibility and more customers. Our website consulting team is personal, easy to work with, and committed to helping you obtain more customers. Improve Your Website Today!</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Web Consulting and Marketing Advice</span></h4>\n\n<p>When you&rsquo;ve got capable employees willing to learn, they just need the proper knowledge and guidance to begin producing results. By using our consulting services, you can get guidance from our marketing specialist and utilize your team. We can teach your team search engine guidelines, web marketing strategies, and which tools to measure the success of your marketing campaign.</p>\n\n<p>Explore our services page to better understand our services and the advantages they provide. We are not interested in one transaction, but are committed to become your long-term web solutions team. Our motto is &ldquo;Turning strangers into friends, and friends into lifelong customers.&rdquo; Don&rsquo;t gamble with your business, talk to someone that knows and cares&hellip;</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 05:37:27',6,NULL,NULL),
	(7,'2','2',NULL,'digital marketing','img/site.png','img/contents/5ea1cadcda89098465935dedb068ab0a.jpg','If your website doesn’t come up on Google search results, how will anybody knows it exists? SEO (Search Engine Optimization) is a tool that brings visibility and in turn traffic to a website.','0','<p>Our optimisation strategy is based on robust market analysis that our SEO experts conduct at the very start of the project. All the SEO techniques we apply are fully compliant with the industry standards. These are just some of the things that set Traffic apart from other run-of-the-mill SEO companies in the worldSEO strategy. To impress Google&rsquo;s SERP, you need a strategy - full of diverse techniques and high quality practices. Only a good strategy can see your SEO through. At Traffic, we specialize in helping businesses mastermind and implement digital marketing strategies. Using a blend of conventional and advanced SEO techniques, we ensure your website ranks high for terms relevant for your specific business.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:rgb(43, 127, 233)\">SEO strategy</span></h4>\n\n<p>To impress Google&rsquo;s SERP, you need a strategy - full of diverse techniques and high quality practices. Only a good strategy can see your SEO through.</p>\n\n<p>At Traffic, we specialize in helping businesses mastermind and implement digital marketing strategies. Using a blend of conventional and advanced SEO techniques, we ensure your website ranks high for terms relevant for your specific business</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">SEO keyword </span></h4>\n\n<p>Research Keyword is an integral element of SEO. It is a delicate science involving research into search patterns, keyword relevancy, market analysis, and even consumer behavior. Do things right and you&rsquo;ll have a firm foundation for your entire SEO campaign; do things wrong and your SEO campaign will become a money pit.</p>\n\n<p>At Traffic, we specialize in smart keyword research. We offer advice on all aspects of your SEO strategy, and help you conduct detailed, insightful keyword research to get everything started the &#39;right&#39; way. Being a local SEO company, we understand regional search patters, and how these variances can boost up your site&rsquo;s SEO.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Competitor analysis </span></h4>\n\n<p>Clever SEO involves digging into your competition&rsquo;s back link profile, conducting content audits, domain analysis to see what they are doing. Using this information to make your digital marketing even smarter is an essential ingredient of cost effective SEO.</p>\n\n<p>Traffic, being a clever SEO agency, enables you keep an eye on your biggest competitors, and helps you beat them. We understand that it isn&rsquo;t always the flashiest websites that&rsquo;s doing the most active trade &ndash; treats emerge from the unlikeliest of sources. Our SEO helps you counter these hidden threats.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">On site SEO </span></h4>\n\n<p>Selecting the right keywords and competition analysis is half the battle, turning this information into a workable &ldquo;on site/on page&rdquo; SEO plan is the key to success.</p>\n\n<p>Traffic&rsquo;s SEO not only helps you to improve your website, but also enables you to match keywords with target pages. By assisting you to enhance site accessibility, loading time, and architectural structure, we assist you to create a killer SEO campaign. Find out more about our design expertise.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Off site SEO </span></h4>\n\n<p>Once the site is ready, SEOs start building links to open the site up for traffic. Linking building is not exactly a science, it is an art, which takes years to master. Simply building irrelevant links, can actually lead your site into trouble.</p>\n\n<p>From writing quality guest posts, to placing links on credible site, and social sharing &ndash; we know many offsite SEO tricks.</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 05:37:00',7,NULL,NULL),
	(30,'1','1',NULL,'news','img/settings.png',NULL,'our team cover a wide range of technology topics, including smartphones, tablets, software, security, operating systems, mobile, storage, servers and data centers, and technology companies, such as Microsoft, Google and Apple.','our team cover a wide range of technology topics, including smartphones, tablets, software, security, operating systems, mobile, storage, servers and data centers, and technology companies, such as Microsoft, Google and Apple.','news','','1',NULL,2,NULL,NULL),
	(8,'2','2',NULL,'email marketing','img/applications.png','img/contents/18e0652bf58416c24d33f50de0cfb89d.jpg','is by far the most frequently used (and misused) digital communications channel by organisations, either bigger or smaller to bring their products to everyone.','0','<p>New, trackable communication methods have kickstarted the region&rsquo;s transition to an online world, with computer, tablet and smart phone developments making this a seamless process for the great majority of us. 31% of Middle East internet users now subscribe to email newsletters relating to companies and brands, while 20% have made purchases as a direct result of an email newsletter.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Integral</span>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<p>For many businesses, email marketing is an integral tool in their digital marketing strategy. An ease of access to return on investment (ROI) figures partnered with the generation of a wealth of metrics makes for one of the most successful channels in the digital marketer&rsquo;s current arsenal. With 84% of GCC based companies stating an increase in their digital marketing budgets by up to 50% within the coming year, it is only set to become an even more influential means of communication.</p>\n\n<p>However, many organisations fail to optimise their email marketing strategies often resulting in email campaigns that do more harm than good.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Data Base&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>We are often asked &ldquo;So how much do you charge for an email list&rdquo; and our answer is always the same. We don&rsquo;t charge anything because we don&rsquo;t sell or rent email lists, we help you to develop your own targeted and relevant database. By doing so, we help to ensure that the people who receive emails from you want to do so and are interested in you, your products or your services, increasing open and click through rates.</p>\n\n<p>With an abundance of unsolicited, unappealing and annoying emails currently flooding the inboxes of internet users, it doesn&rsquo;t take much to turn potential customers into brand saboteurs, making it that much harder to develop meaningful relationships with these potential customers.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Our email marketing suite</span></h4>\n\n<p>Our system allows you to generate and send out high quality HTML emails based on pre designed templates within minutes and with absolutely no technical knowledge. We help segment your database into groups based on your individual needs. For example, if you have an offer which is relevant to male members of the Saudi market, aged 24-35 who have purchased products from you within the last 6 months, we can ensure your promotion reaches exactly this audience.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 05:37:43',8,NULL,NULL),
	(21,'1','3',NULL,'More than a million people are using Slack every day now','img/contents/1eaca03bfefa38e472fb815501de097d.png','img/contents/fbb87937bbb5e43f3e0678dcc4bbbbbb.png','More than a million people use Slack every day now. You do, probably. Hard to imagine you reading a story about enterprise software if it wasn’t a part of your working life.','<p>More than a million people use Slack every day now. You do, probably. Hard to imagine you reading a story about enterprise software if it wasn&rsquo;t a part of your working life. Then again, Slack has always been a little weird like that. A year and a half ago, no one had ever heard of it. A few days later, everyone you knew was using it.</p>\n','<p>Okay, not&nbsp;<em>everyone</em>. But all the startups had taken their workplace chatter there, and then the media did, too. And once something is being used by all of the startups and all of the media, it begins to feel inevitable and then necessary. (This is the entire story of Twitter.)</p>\n\n<p>300,000 OF SLACK&#39;S 1.1 MILLION USERS USE THE PAID VERSION</p>\n\n<p>Of Slack&rsquo;s 1.1 million users, 300,000 use the paid version. Employers will pay between $6.67 and $48 a month per user for the hottest Slack features, such as a searchable archive with unlimited messages ($6.67 a month, if billed annually); an archive of everything you have ever typed, for compliance purposes ($12.50 a month, billed annually) and &quot;a configurable email ingestion service,&quot; $48, which sounds disgusting.</p>\n\n<p>Slack projects its revenues around $25 million this year. It has raised $340 million, and&nbsp;is valued at $2.8 billion. At least, that&rsquo;s how much it was worth in April. Who knows what it would be valued at today. Pick any number you like &mdash; $8 billion, say. Slack will probably be worth that at some point. November, maybe?</p>\n\n<p>SLACK WILL GENERATE REVENUES OF $25 MILLION THIS YEAR</p>\n\n<p>Some people use Slack for free. There is a writers&rsquo; Slack, and an LGBTQ Slack, and a Slack for former Twitter employees, who hang out in Slack all day long and LOL at the day&rsquo;s Twitter news.&nbsp;There is ChitCats, &quot;a place to discover and join private Slack groups,&quot; where people vote on Slacks, Reddit-style.</p>\n\n<p>This week a group named Free Code Camp sent me an email with the promising subject line &quot;Slack is lying to its users.&quot; The founder of Free Code Camp, Quincy Larson, complained that while Slack promises it is free to an&nbsp;<em>unlimited</em>&nbsp;number of users, this week code campers reached the previously undocumented free Slack limit of 8,462 people. A spokeswoman for Slack said this: &quot;Slack plainly says about the free plan, &lsquo;We offer a free plan for small teams, casual users, and anyone who wants to evaluate Slack.&rsquo; Based on that, it&rsquo;s difficult to infer Slack would be an appropriate tool for use by a 10,000-person community.&quot;</p>\n\n<p>Slack&rsquo;s&nbsp;pricing&nbsp;page&nbsp;really does say there are &quot;no limits on time or users,&quot; though, so at some point Slack will have to change the language there. It won&rsquo;t be that big of a deal.</p>\n\n<p>FREE UP TO 8,462 USERS</p>\n\n<p>Slack is successful because it integrates with other things &mdash; about 100 other things right now. Workplace chat apps are a dime a dozen, so as best as anyone can tell, it&rsquo;s these integrations that made Slack a big deal. For example, you can set up a chat room that tells you every time people mention your #brand on Twitter. (Your brand sucks!) Or you can set up a room that imports every picture that Beyonc&eacute; posts to Instagram. Or you can have Github do things in your Slack, if you are a code person. Slack users have set up 900,000 of these integrations so far, and they send 30 million messages a week.</p>\n\n<p>Slack is not perfect. Months ago, its founder, Stewart Butterfield, told me you would soon be able to leave emoji comments on Slack messages. For example, if someone said something poopy, you could comment with a poop emoji, and so could your co-workers, and in time you would return to view the poopy message, and it would have eight poops next to it. This hasn&rsquo;t shipped yet, and I for one would like to know what&rsquo;s going on there.</p>\n\n<p>Slack also leads employees to&nbsp;near-constant goofing around, whether by playing games of Jeopardy! or using Giphy to punctuate every sentence with random animations. John Herrman memorably called this &quot;mainstream work larping.&quot;&nbsp;Certainly you will observe people at your company who never have time for&nbsp;<em>you</em>&nbsp;but are incredibly active on Slack, hunting through every chat room in search of someone to banter with for a few more moments before returning to their TPS reports.</p>\n\n<p>A PERSISTENT LOW-LEVEL WORK ANXIETY THAT WILL HAUNT YOU UNTIL THE END OF TIME</p>\n\n<p>But you will also observe people who barely pay attention to Slack at all, and you will resent them for it, and at some point someone you work with who is terrible at Slack will be fired for not being &quot;a culture fit,&quot; and you&rsquo;ll understand that these two things are likely related. How much should you participate in Slack? What is the right amount of GIFs? These will add to the persistent, low-level work anxieties that you will carry around for the rest of your days.</p>\n\n<p>On the other hand, look at Google Docs. Until&nbsp;<em>very</em>&nbsp;recently &mdash; yesterday, maybe? &mdash; opening a Google Doc through Slack took three clicks. The first click opened a useless sidebar. The second click opened a browser tab that contained a link to the Google Doc in a format that looked exactly like the tab in the useless sidebar. Then you clicked&nbsp;<em>that</em>link and finally your Google Doc opened. I asked Slack to fix this on Twitter last week, and a couple people chimed in, and this morning when I went to open a Google Doc through Slack, it opened with a single click.</p>\n\n<p>Anyway, 1.1 million people, $25 million, $2.8 billion. The numbers look big today. They won&rsquo;t tomorrow.</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 12:37:16',NULL,NULL,NULL),
	(9,'1','2',NULL,'Mobile','img/mobile.png','img/contents/92f25c75f02c1396c50d4d89a1c42f42.png','We ensure elegant, straightforward & enjoyable user experiences on desktops, tablets,  smartphones & any other smart devices.   ','<p>What is an app? The term &ldquo;app&rdquo; is short for &ldquo;application&rdquo;. Within digital marketing, when we refer to an app, we are generally talking about a mobile application such as those that you, and millions of others, use every day on smart phones around the world, or a campaign application on your corporate Facebook page. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>When strategically developed and targeted, custom Facebook applications can support your outbound and inbound marketing or business goals with trackable results. With a Facebook population of over 22 million across the Middle East there&rsquo;s no question that your audience is ready.</p>\n','<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Custom applications</span></h4>\n\n<p>By rolling out unique and engaging promotions across your social media channels, you give your company or brand the ability to engage with your target market in a real and meaningful manner, increasing reach of information and customer conversion.</p>\n\n<p>A key benefit of custom applications, is the ability to gather user data as part of the process. &nbsp;This data can then be used to stay in touch with your audience, to drive key business decisions and to help direct your marketing strategies.</p>\n\n<p>How many people within your customer base are between the ages of 25 and 34? How many of these customers are male or female? How many live in Bahrain, Saudi Arabia or the greater GCC area? Any number of questions can be posed and answered giving you incredible insight into your target market.</p>\n\n<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Keep it simple</span></h4>\n\n<p>We have rolled out a whole raft of custom applications for our customers, ranging from simple sign ups with custom landing pages, ensuring that your visitors are prompted to become a part of your community before being able to participate, through to fully customised treasure hunts, leading users to engage with each and every online and offline marketing channel available. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>We have learnt that the key to a successful campaign is ensuring that, no matter how many channels you wish to activate, the barriers to entry are as few as possible and that requirements necessary to engage are as simple as possible.</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Return of investment</span></h4>\n\n<p>Of course, a core concept of digital and social media marketing is the ability to track and analyse your return on investment. We ensure that, for every custom campaign developed, we track all the key analytical touch points you would expect: How many people visited the page? How many users clicked on the links? How many users shared content? How many users converted into fans? etc.</p>\n\n<p>By comparing this information against details gathered either before or after the campaign, we are able to assign a baseline to your standard traffic and conversion, therefore assigning any gains to activities undertaken in association with your campaign. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For a clear example of an effective custom Facebook application, check out our case study on the &lsquo;Be A Part of Our History&rsquo; 2013 Porsche Boxster campaign.</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-06-29 11:06:13',9,NULL,NULL),
	(10,'2','2',NULL,'social media','img/keyboard.png','img/contents/ddf03cf9f95b2f1c8913fdedd9997227.jpg','The use of social media throughout the Middle East has exploded in recent years, with a diverse demographic of users embracing mainstream channels such as Facebook, Twitter, YouTube, LinkedIn and more.','0','<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Social domination</span></h4>\n\n<p>The Middle East&rsquo;s internet usage is dominated by social networking and email, with some 88% of users actively engaging in social networking on a daily basis. With 34% making purchases through online channels, it&rsquo;s clear that the buying process for many consumers is heavily influenced by what is being said on social networking channels. This is made even clearer when you consider that 73% of internet users in the GCC state that their decision to buy products and services has been influenced by online reviews and discussions.</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">The stats have it&nbsp;</span></h4>\n\n<p>Platforms such as Facebook, Twitter and YouTube are teeming with social activity from regional users and contain established communities that represent many organisations&rsquo; target audiences. Throughout the GCC alone the Facebook penetration rate has been measured at 98% of internet users, while Twitter has a penetration of 36%. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>61% of internet users in the GCC actively discuss brands, products and services through online mediums, whether on social networks, forums or blogs. Their opinions can be shared with hundred or even thousands of other internet browsers &ndash; essentially the internet has allowed anyone with an opinion to be heard by a very large audience if they choose to make their opinions public.</p>\n\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<h4><span style=\"color:#2B7FE9\">Maintenance &amp; Opmisation</span></h4>\n\n<p>Our approach to social media marketing aims to develop authentic, two-way communications. We have learnt that creating relevant online communities consisting of engaged stakeholders and consumers is what leads to revenue generation. Combining individual research with our experience and expertise, we take a holistic approach that combines strategic goal setting, public relations and community management, making sure our clients receive the full benefit of having a great social media presence. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Clients such as Audi, Spring of Culture and Porsche have benefited from our services &ndash; view case studies here.</p>\n','g-ocanto','0','2015-07-02 07:37:00',10,NULL,NULL),
